snippet.title: Leave Me Alone! trailer 2
snippet.description:
Leave Me Alone! is a game based on evasion and survival. You are being chased mercilessly and must outmanoeuvre your pursuer for as long as you can. Lose them amongst the endless obstacles and use power-ups and magic hats along the way to help you get as far as possible.

Play for free now!
